Dialogue: 1,0:08:44.54,0:08:46.41,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,鈴 放再低點
Dialogue: 1,0:08:46.94,0:08:48.35,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,要起風了動作快點
Dialogue: 1,0:08:48.66,0:08:49.18,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 1,0:08:50.42,0:08:52.86,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,媽媽 給我2錢
Dialogue: 1,0:08:52.95,0:08:54.59,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我鉛筆掉了
Dialogue: 1,0:08:54.65,0:08:56.39,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,在發零花錢前給我忍下
Dialogue: 1,0:08:57.57,0:09:00.00,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你別再亂畫畫不就得了
Dialogue: 1,0:09:03.06,0:09:05.61,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,澄 我跟你換支鉛筆吧
Dialogue: 1,0:09:05.67,0:09:06.17,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不了
Dialogue: 1,0:09:06.27,0:09:07.00,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,鈴
Dialogue: 1,0:09:07.20,0:09:10.06,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,水原家的哲 每天都有去學校嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:09:10.34,0:09:11.90,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,嗯？有來呀
Dialogue: 1,0:09:17.56,0:09:18.25,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,好冷
Dialogue: 1,0:09:18.25,0:09:19.21,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,好冷
Dialogue: 1,0:09:38.02,0:09:38.73,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 1,0:09:40.67,0:09:42.12,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,好短
Dialogue: 1,0:09:42.61,0:09:44.80,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不知道這樣能不能撐過這週
Dialogue: 1,0:09:45.17,0:09:47.26,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,這次別丟了才行
Dialogue: 1,0:09:50.96,0:09:52.93,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,今天的畫是自由畫
Dialogue: 1,0:09:53.36,0:09:55.67,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,交了的人就可以回去了
Dialogue: 1,0:09:55.70,0:09:56.96,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 1,0:09:56.96,0:09:58.53,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,要畫哪裡好呢
Dialogue: 1,0:09:58.53,0:09:59.80,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,哪裡好呢
Dialogue: 1,0:10:00.62,0:10:02.25,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,嗯 不錯哦
Dialogue: 1,0:10:02.62,0:10:03.99,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不愧是你
Dialogue: 1,0:10:04.60,0:10:06.76,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,真好啊小鈴 畫這麼好看
Dialogue: 1,0:10:09.44,0:10:11.20,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 1,0:10:13.43,0:10:15.63,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那我去撿枯松葉了
Dialogue: 1,0:10:15.81,0:10:16.84,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,拜託你了
Dialogue: 1,0:10:35.90,0:10:37.25,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,水原
Dialogue: 1,0:10:37.81,0:10:41.33,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你再不畫的話就回不去了喲
Dialogue: 1,0:10:41.84,0:10:42.49,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我不回去
Dialogue: 1,0:10:43.72,0:10:47.09,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,爸爸媽媽也不採海苔 只會喝酒
Dialogue: 1,0:10:47.74,0:10:49.03,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我討厭大海
Dialogue: 1,0:10:49.84,0:10:50.77,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不畫
Dialogue: 1,0:10:51.32,0:10:52.73,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,浦野 手伸出來
Dialogue: 1,0:10:57.34,0:10:57.73,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 1,0:10:57.77,0:10:58.20,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,給你
Dialogue: 1,0:11:00.96,0:11:02.00,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不過
Dialogue: 1,0:11:02.45,0:11:05.08,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我哥哥的 我還有很多
Dialogue: 1,0:11:05.66,0:11:07.29,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,兔子在跳著
Dialogue: 1,0:11:08.12,0:11:11.32,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,正月的沉沒事故發生時也是這樣的大海
Dialogue: 1,0:11:12.24,0:11:13.94,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,要畫的話你來畫吧
Dialogue: 1,0:11:14.44,0:11:15.87,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,畫這個無趣的大海
Dialogue: 1,0:11:18.99,0:11:22.30,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,水原 你剛剛說的是什麼意思
Dialogue: 1,0:11:25.29,0:11:27.89,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,白浪就像跳動的兔子一樣
Dialogue: 1,0:11:28.72,0:11:31.54,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,水原 給你加上哥哥吧
Dialogue: 1,0:11:31.55,0:11:32.22,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 1,0:11:33.22,0:11:35.90,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,給你哥哥看見的話要全速逃跑
Dialogue: 1,0:11:35.90,0:11:37.63,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我們男生間有這樣的規定
Dialogue: 1,0:11:40.08,0:11:43.55,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不過…也比進入海軍學校
Dialogue: 1,0:11:44.21,0:11:46.50,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,然後在海裡溺死的笨蛋要好
Dialogue: 1,0:11:48.07,0:11:51.69,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,真的誒 就像白色的兔子一樣
Dialogue: 1,0:11:53.31,0:11:54.98,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,嗯 畫好了
Dialogue: 1,0:11:55.52,0:11:56.80,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,幫你撿好了
Dialogue: 1,0:11:56.80,0:11:57.93,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 1,0:11:59.87,0:12:01.69,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,很好哦 畫得真棒
Dialogue: 1,0:12:02.58,0:12:04.95,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,既然都畫好了那只能回去了
Dialogue: 1,0:12:05.94,0:12:06.86,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,這樣的畫
Dialogue: 1,0:12:07.82,0:12:09.58,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不就討厭不起這個海了
