Dialogue: 1,0:57:57.32,0:58:03.83,kono-text-year,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1444,834)\fs60\fn@方正粗雅宋_GBK\c&HE7E5E5&\bord0.1\blur5\pos(335,302)\3c&H464646&}9
Dialogue: 1,0:57:57.32,0:58:03.83,kono-text-year,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1444,834)\fs70\fn@方正粗雅宋_GBK\frz270.8\c&HE7E5E5&\bord0.1\blur5\pos(309,347.224)\3c&H464646&}月
Dialogue: 1,0:58:01.25,0:58:02.50,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,天還很熱
Dialogue: 1,0:58:04.32,0:58:05.84,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,北條家的媳婦
Dialogue: 1,0:58:06.32,0:58:07.73,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,有打給你的電話
Dialogue: 1,0:58:09.13,0:58:11.54,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,來了 給我的電話嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:58:15.03,0:58:16.04,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,啊 這個這個
Dialogue: 1,0:58:17.77,0:58:19.20,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,好熱
Dialogue: 1,0:58:19.37,0:58:21.10,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,受到蒙羞的人是周作
Dialogue: 1,0:58:21.10,0:58:22.37,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你啊 就這個樣子出門…
Dialogue: 1,0:58:32.66,0:58:35.20,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,就在附近 稍微走一走吧
Dialogue: 1,0:58:35.59,0:58:38.74,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,然後 GKF的情況如何
Dialogue: 1,0:58:35.59,0:58:38.74,kono-text-cn - tips,,0,0,0,,註: GKF指南西方面艦隊
Dialogue: 1,0:58:38.98,0:58:40.19,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,現在是很空閒的樣子
Dialogue: 1,0:58:40.19,0:58:41.07,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 1,0:58:41.28,0:58:42.75,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,嘛 先去喝點冰啤酒吧
Dialogue: 1,0:58:59.54,0:59:02.57,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,周作 我給你送筆記本來了
Dialogue: 1,0:59:08.52,0:59:09.48,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,鈴
Dialogue: 1,0:59:10.22,0:59:12.12,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,塗得好白啊 沒問題吧
Dialogue: 1,0:59:13.23,0:59:14.91,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,會不會很奇怪呀
Dialogue: 1,0:59:16.00,0:59:17.88,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,沒事 精神就好
Dialogue: 1,0:59:18.59,0:59:19.75,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我們走吧
Dialogue: 1,0:59:21.57,0:59:22.38,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,工作怎麼辦
Dialogue: 1,0:59:22.97,0:59:26.20,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,明明不是很急 卻特意幫我把筆記本拿過來
Dialogue: 1,0:59:27.28,0:59:30.14,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你說過到鎮上買東西很開心對吧
Dialogue: 1,0:59:34.40,0:59:35.17,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 1,0:59:35.86,0:59:36.94,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,果然身體有什麼…
Dialogue: 1,0:59:37.28,0:59:39.34,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,在偷偷樂而已啦
Dialogue: 1,0:59:45.23,0:59:47.24,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,本來還想著看電影
Dialogue: 1,0:59:49.63,0:59:52.32,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,剛好有艘大船回港了
Dialogue: 1,0:59:54.76,0:59:56.40,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,沒辦法 只能讓給他們看了
Dialogue: 1,0:59:57.32,0:59:59.54,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,雖然有點可惜 還是等下一次吧
Dialogue: 1,1:00:02.81,1:00:03.87,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,鈴？
Dialogue: 1,1:00:04.34,1:00:09.01,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,小學同年級的有成為水兵的
Dialogue: 1,1:00:09.58,1:00:11.99,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,見到了不知道要怎麼辦好…
Dialogue: 1,1:00:12.15,1:00:14.55,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,普通地打招呼不就行了
Dialogue: 1,1:00:15.58,1:00:18.16,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,如果現在跟以前認識的人見了面的話
Dialogue: 1,1:00:18.35,1:00:22.25,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我會不會就從夢裡醒來了呢
Dialogue: 1,1:00:22.66,1:00:23.54,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,夢…
Dialogue: 1,1:00:23.86,1:00:27.76,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,住所跟姓氏都變了 淨是讓人為難的事
Dialogue: 1,1:00:28.01,1:00:31.09,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不過即使如此 能有周作對我好
Dialogue: 1,1:00:31.26,1:00:33.04,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,而且還交到了朋友
Dialogue: 1,1:00:33.83,1:00:36.95,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,嗯… 現在醒來的話就不有趣了
Dialogue: 1,1:00:37.45,1:00:40.16,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,如果現在的我就是真正的我 那就挺好的
Dialogue: 1,1:00:40.37,1:00:41.61,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 1,1:00:42.91,1:00:45.47,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,過去的事 沒選擇的道路
Dialogue: 1,1:00:46.16,1:00:49.01,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,都跟醒來時結束的夢沒兩樣
Dialogue: 1,1:00:49.71,1:00:52.37,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,鈴 選擇了你
Dialogue: 1,1:00:52.61,1:00:55.07,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,對我來說很可能是最好的選擇了
Dialogue: 1,1:00:57.00,1:00:59.94,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,只不過你好像有點瘦了 真讓人擔心
Dialogue: 1,1:01:00.58,1:01:04.55,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,說起來 最近好像沒什麼胃口…
Dialogue: 1,1:01:11.50,1:01:13.26,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,給 2人份
Dialogue: 1,1:01:20.38,1:01:22.66,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,畢竟早上白白地多吃了那麼多
Dialogue: 1,1:01:22.81,1:01:24.76,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,大概這個量應該夠了吧
Dialogue: 1,1:01:26.79,1:01:28.58,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,果然還是一人的分量
Dialogue: 1,1:01:28.99,1:01:35.56,kono-text-year,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1447,834)\fs50\fn方正粗雅宋_GBK\c&HE7E5E5&\pos(331,360)}1944
Dialogue: 1,1:01:28.99,1:01:35.56,kono-text-year,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1447,834)\fs70\fn@方正粗雅宋_GBK\frz270.8\c&HE7E5E5&\pos(303,410)}年
Dialogue: 1,1:01:28.99,1:01:35.56,kono-text-year,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1447,834)\fs60\fn@方正粗雅宋_GBK\c&HE7E5E5&\pos(331,508.542)}12
Dialogue: 1,1:01:28.99,1:01:35.56,kono-text-year,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1447,834)\fs70\fn@方正粗雅宋_GBK\frz270.8\c&HE7E5E5&\pos(303,549.224)}月
Dialogue: 1,1:01:28.83,1:01:35.40,kono-text-cn - tips,,0,0,0,,註：日本海軍自衛隊 紅表示減速 黑表示加速
Dialogue: 1,1:01:28.83,1:01:32.82,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,準備入港 前進低速 紅20
Dialogue: 1,1:01:33.08,1:01:35.40,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,航向不變 低速整定 紅20
Dialogue: 1,1:01:35.40,1:01:37.10,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,航向不變
Dialogue: 1,1:01:39.38,1:01:41.28,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,之後我會幫你試著拜託他的
Dialogue: 1,1:01:43.49,1:01:44.32,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 1,1:01:45.02,1:01:47.90,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,是真正的水兵
Dialogue: 1,1:01:49.38,1:01:52.36,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,在井口那邊突然遇見的
Dialogue: 1,1:01:52.70,1:01:53.88,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我是水原哲
Dialogue: 1,1:01:54.25,1:01:55.87,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,軍艦青葉的船員
Dialogue: 1,1:01:56.68,1:01:58.91,kono-text-cn - tips,,0,0,0,,註：甲型巡洋艦 或 一等巡洋艦
Dialogue: 1,1:01:56.68,1:01:58.91,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,青葉的話是甲巡吧
Dialogue: 1,1:01:59.66,1:02:01.51,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,喂 晴美
Dialogue: 1,1:02:04.97,1:02:07.50,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,冬天也還曬得那麼黑
Dialogue: 1,1:02:07.65,1:02:11.16,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那麼 你是來我們家泡澡的嗎
Dialogue: 1,1:02:11.32,1:02:14.21,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,嗯 現在是叫做泡澡登陸的自由時間
Dialogue: 1,1:02:14.69,1:02:16.68,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,也沒什麼想去的地方
Dialogue: 1,1:02:16.87,1:02:19.57,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,所以就依靠了同鄉的鈴 來這裡打擾了
Dialogue: 1,1:02:20.16,1:02:22.61,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,謝謝各位對鈴的照顧
Dialogue: 1,1:02:23.89,1:02:27.78,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,鈴從以前除了畫畫跟製作乾海苔就沒什麼優點
Dialogue: 1,1:02:27.84,1:02:30.02,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,現在也只是個呆瓜吧
Dialogue: 1,1:02:30.56,1:02:32.97,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,如果大家不客氣地跟我講的話
Dialogue: 1,1:02:32.99,1:02:34.39,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我就把她帶回去了
Dialogue: 1,1:02:39.24,1:02:41.27,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,要裝腔作勢也得有個限度
Dialogue: 1,1:02:41.31,1:02:43.68,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,還「鈴 鈴」地直呼名字
Dialogue: 1,1:02:44.78,1:02:46.33,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那要怎麼稱呼才好
Dialogue: 1,1:02:46.66,1:02:48.26,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你不都已經不是浦野了麼
Dialogue: 1,1:02:49.83,1:02:52.55,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,鈴 不能對水兵這麼粗魯
Dialogue: 1,1:03:02.49,1:03:03.99,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,有什麼好笑的嗎
Dialogue: 1,1:03:04.02,1:03:07.39,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,好笑啊 你真是普通啊
Dialogue: 1,1:03:07.84,1:03:09.88,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,好吃 嗯 好吃
Dialogue: 1,1:03:09.89,1:03:11.36,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,粗茶淡飯而已
Dialogue: 1,1:03:11.43,1:03:13.41,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,真是愜意
Dialogue: 1,1:03:13.77,1:03:15.92,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,喂 鈴也進來吧
Dialogue: 1,1:03:16.16,1:03:17.24,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你傻嗎
Dialogue: 1,1:03:17.58,1:03:19.82,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,鈴 煤油燈在哪
Dialogue: 1,1:03:20.42,1:03:22.81,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,好像是在防空壕裡面
Dialogue: 1,1:03:22.90,1:03:23.54,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 1,1:03:25.16,1:03:27.79,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,晴美將來也要成為水兵
Dialogue: 1,1:03:28.41,1:03:30.01,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那樣太好了
Dialogue: 1,1:03:30.01,1:03:30.99,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,給
Dialogue: 1,1:03:31.36,1:03:32.25,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那就不客氣了
Dialogue: 1,1:03:32.90,1:03:33.87,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,招呼呢
Dialogue: 1,1:03:34.19,1:03:35.56,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 1,1:03:36.46,1:03:37.80,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 1,1:03:40.05,1:03:41.75,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,陸地上就是好
Dialogue: 1,1:03:41.86,1:03:43.46,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那麼我就
Dialogue: 1,1:03:44.36,1:03:46.73,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,青葉怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 1,1:03:47.12,1:03:50.48,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,在馬尼拉負傷 歷盡艱辛終於回來了
Dialogue: 1,1:03:50.83,1:03:55.25,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,明明是一艘好艦 卻又要遠離戰場默默無聞了
Dialogue: 1,1:03:57.23,1:03:58.54,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我說周作啊
Dialogue: 1,1:03:59.09,1:04:02.81,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,苟且偷生真是讓人焦躁
Dialogue: 1,1:04:04.74,1:04:05.90,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,水原
Dialogue: 1,1:04:06.19,1:04:10.01,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,因為父親有夜勤不回來 今晚我就是家主
Dialogue: 1,1:04:10.56,1:04:14.14,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,雖然對不起你 但是我不能讓你在這裡過夜
Dialogue: 1,1:04:18.79,1:04:19.33,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 1,1:04:19.82,1:04:21.74,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,讓他睡農具房2樓了
Dialogue: 1,1:04:22.56,1:04:24.21,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,真是稀奇
Dialogue: 1,1:04:24.51,1:04:26.80,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你也有這麼強勢的時候
Dialogue: 1,1:04:28.69,1:04:29.10,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,給
Dialogue: 1,1:04:29.58,1:04:32.08,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,腳爐開了 給他帶去吧
Dialogue: 1,1:04:32.41,1:04:34.31,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,然後慢慢跟他聊天吧
Dialogue: 1,1:04:34.55,1:04:36.16,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,也許再也見不到了
Dialogue: 1,1:04:51.41,1:04:53.39,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,對不起 讓你在這裡睡
Dialogue: 1,1:04:54.66,1:04:56.70,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,跟吊床比算是特別舒服了
Dialogue: 1,1:04:57.43,1:04:59.30,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,誒 有很多要聊的吧
Dialogue: 1,1:05:00.02,1:05:01.54,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,天很冷 腳先放進去吧
Dialogue: 1,1:05:06.19,1:05:08.66,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,給你 是禮物
Dialogue: 1,1:05:08.94,1:05:09.65,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,哎呀
Dialogue: 1,1:05:12.70,1:05:13.79,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,要做成羽毛筆嗎
Dialogue: 1,1:05:16.22,1:05:16.78,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 1,1:05:25.65,1:05:27.16,kono-text-cn-2,,0,0,0,,寫得出來啊
Dialogue: 1,1:05:25.29,1:05:27.16,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,寫得出寫得出
Dialogue: 1,1:05:28.16,1:05:29.88,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,雖然看著像鷺的羽毛
Dialogue: 1,1:05:29.95,1:05:32.58,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,然而畢竟當時見到的時候是在南部的海上
Dialogue: 1,1:05:32.70,1:05:35.24,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,鷺會渡海嗎
Dialogue: 1,1:05:35.48,1:05:36.72,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,對吧
Dialogue: 1,1:05:36.96,1:05:40.73,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,畢竟在江波那邊可是一整年都只在河上面站著
Dialogue: 1,1:05:42.04,1:05:44.00,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,以前在江波真的很多
Dialogue: 1,1:05:45.58,1:05:46.81,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,總覺得不太行
Dialogue: 1,1:05:46.93,1:05:48.54,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,沒法按想像中的來畫
Dialogue: 1,1:05:49.28,1:05:51.01,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你也有這種時候的嗎
Dialogue: 1,1:05:52.57,1:05:53.56,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,難不成
Dialogue: 1,1:05:54.22,1:05:55.97,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,很久沒畫了嗎
Dialogue: 1,1:05:56.16,1:05:57.18,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,算是吧…
Dialogue: 1,1:05:59.07,1:06:00.02,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那幅畫
Dialogue: 1,1:06:00.76,1:06:02.43,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那些波浪的白兔
Dialogue: 1,1:06:03.82,1:06:04.55,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 1,1:06:05.58,1:06:07.68,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,畢竟那之後真是不得了了
Dialogue: 1,1:06:09.27,1:06:10.27,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,是嗎？
Dialogue: 1,1:06:11.28,1:06:12.86,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你忘了嗎？
Dialogue: 1,1:06:13.28,1:06:16.71,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,老師把那幅畫放到廣島市的比賽裡參賽
Dialogue: 1,1:06:17.15,1:06:19.61,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,然後好評如潮
Dialogue: 1,1:06:20.06,1:06:21.55,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我當時真的很為難
Dialogue: 1,1:06:22.64,1:06:25.04,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,畢竟大家都認為是我畫的
Dialogue: 1,1:06:25.73,1:06:27.43,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,真正的功勞
Dialogue: 1,1:06:27.61,1:06:28.92,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,明明是你
Dialogue: 1,1:06:38.28,1:06:40.29,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,鈴真暖
Dialogue: 1,1:06:40.73,1:06:42.71,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,鈴真柔弱
Dialogue: 1,1:06:42.84,1:06:44.04,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,真香
Dialogue: 1,1:06:48.16,1:06:49.34,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,水原
Dialogue: 1,1:06:50.97,1:06:54.11,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我感覺自己一直在等著這樣的日子
Dialogue: 1,1:06:55.39,1:06:57.60,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你能這樣過來
Dialogue: 1,1:06:58.59,1:07:00.46,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,明明距離自己那麼近
Dialogue: 1,1:07:01.17,1:07:02.09,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 1,1:07:04.03,1:07:07.81,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我真的 被那個人給氣死了
Dialogue: 1,1:07:08.81,1:07:09.61,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 1,1:07:10.08,1:07:11.72,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,真的對不起
Dialogue: 1,1:07:12.91,1:07:16.16,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你…喜歡那個人吧
Dialogue: 1,1:07:16.92,1:07:17.62,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 1,1:07:20.05,1:07:22.31,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,真是普通得讓人吃驚
Dialogue: 1,1:07:22.57,1:07:23.30,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 1,1:07:23.41,1:07:25.88,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,簡直像為理所當然的事情生氣
Dialogue: 1,1:07:26.10,1:07:28.40,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,為理所當然的事情道著歉一樣
Dialogue: 1,1:07:29.15,1:07:31.09,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不帶你回去真的沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 1,1:07:31.61,1:07:34.52,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不是因為被迫嫁給別人而覺得為難嗎
Dialogue: 1,1:07:36.42,1:07:37.80,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那就好
Dialogue: 1,1:07:40.14,1:07:41.88,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,大4年是吧
Dialogue: 1,1:07:42.64,1:07:43.73,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你說周作？
Dialogue: 1,1:07:44.06,1:07:46.13,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,跟死去的哥哥同歲
Dialogue: 1,1:07:47.68,1:07:49.20,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,因為我家比較窮
Dialogue: 1,1:07:49.34,1:07:52.33,kono-text-cn - tips,,0,0,0,,註：舊大日本帝國海軍培養海軍軍官的軍事學校
Dialogue: 1,1:07:49.34,1:07:52.33,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,哥哥進了免費的海軍兵學校
Dialogue: 1,1:07:53.14,1:07:56.11,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,因為哥哥死了 我也進了海軍
Dialogue: 1,1:07:57.01,1:07:58.90,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,明明全都是理所當然的
Dialogue: 1,1:07:59.21,1:08:03.37,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我也許是哪個地方跟人類的理所當然相背離了
Dialogue: 1,1:08:04.68,1:08:05.51,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,所以說
Dialogue: 1,1:08:06.47,1:08:09.36,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,在這裡看到鈴這麼普通 我放心了
Dialogue: 1,1:08:09.91,1:08:12.64,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我可不想被別人叫做英靈
Dialogue: 1,1:08:13.34,1:08:16.61,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,如果要想起我 就笑著想起我吧
Dialogue: 1,1:08:17.59,1:08:18.98,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,只有你
Dialogue: 1,1:08:19.35,1:08:23.53,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,要在這個世界一直地普通下去正常下去
Dialogue: 1,1:08:24.00,1:08:24.81,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,鈴
Dialogue: 1,1:08:25.55,1:08:27.09,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你變漂亮了
Dialogue: 1,1:08:27.84,1:08:29.24,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你傻嗎
Dialogue: 1,1:08:31.89,1:08:35.51,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,真的從小就開始
Dialogue: 1,1:08:35.73,1:08:38.62,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,對你有著沒法說出重要話的毛病啊
Dialogue: 1,1:08:32.71,1:08:39.67,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(941,0)\fn@方正毡笔黑_gbk\fs60\frz253.4\bord0\c&H85645B&\move(466.877,173.175,579.471,205.598,0,3485)}哲
Dialogue: 1,1:08:32.71,1:08:39.67,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(941,0)\fn@方正毡笔黑_GBK\fs60\frz253.4\bord0\c&H85645B&\move(384.095,261.289,499.36,293.721,0,3485))}羽毛謝謝了
Dialogue: 1,1:08:32.71,1:08:39.67,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(941,0)\fn@方正毡笔黑_GBK\fs60\frz253.4\bord0\c&H85645B&\move(301.314,349.401,419.249,384.494,0,3485)}謝謝你變得那麽優秀
Dialogue: 1,1:08:32.71,1:08:39.67,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(941,0)\fn@方正毡笔黑_GBK\fs60\frz253.4\bord0\c&H85645B&\move(237.224,360.082,360.5,392.505,0,3485)}很高興你能活著來看我
Dialogue: 1,1:08:32.71,1:08:39.67,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(941,0)\fn@方正毡笔黑_GBK\fs60\frz253.4\bord0\c&H85645B&\move(117.058,573.691,243.004,608.784,0,3485)}鈴
Dialogue: 1,1:08:49.83,1:08:51.85,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,歡迎回來 鬼哥
Dialogue: 1,1:08:52.31,1:08:55.92,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,但是用那樣一顆石子來代替屍骨
Dialogue: 1,1:08:56.66,1:08:58.66,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,因為太過小了 小澄竟然…
Dialogue: 1,1:08:58.64,1:09:01.21,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,鬼哥的…腦子？
Dialogue: 1,1:09:01.95,1:09:03.62,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,…這樣搞混了
Dialogue: 1,1:09:04.00,1:09:05.46,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你哥哥是怎樣的人
Dialogue: 1,1:09:06.73,1:09:09.34,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,大冷天的被叫過來 真傻
Dialogue: 1,1:09:09.56,1:09:12.08,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那個要一真的會這麼容易死掉嗎
Dialogue: 1,1:09:13.36,1:09:15.56,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,真沒勁 人總是突然消失了
Dialogue: 1,1:09:16.20,1:09:21.15,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,看不見身影了 就…沒法傳達話語了
Dialogue: 1,1:09:23.04,1:09:24.28,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,周作
Dialogue: 1,1:09:25.57,1:09:28.85,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,前段時間 謝謝你了
Dialogue: 1,1:09:30.23,1:09:33.53,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,給我時間和水原說話
Dialogue: 1,1:09:34.76,1:09:35.61,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,沒…
Dialogue: 1,1:09:36.36,1:09:37.83,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不過 周作
Dialogue: 1,1:09:38.44,1:09:40.02,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,夫婦是那樣的嗎
Dialogue: 1,1:09:42.07,1:09:45.00,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,因為是我硬要讓你嫁過來
Dialogue: 1,1:09:47.28,1:09:49.36,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,但你明明不表現給我看
Dialogue: 1,1:09:49.51,1:09:50.90,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那樣的生氣表情
Dialogue: 1,1:09:51.15,1:09:51.90,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,什…
Dialogue: 1,1:09:52.33,1:09:54.03,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,現在不就在表現給你看嗎
Dialogue: 1,1:09:55.88,1:09:58.26,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,嚯~ 我倒是不知道你會生氣
Dialogue: 1,1:09:58.70,1:10:00.49,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那是你注意力渙散而已
Dialogue: 1,1:10:01.02,1:10:02.14,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,嚯~
Dialogue: 1,1:10:03.92,1:10:07.08,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,所以你今天才穿了破洞的襪子
Dialogue: 1,1:10:07.59,1:10:11.13,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,是因為鈴昨晚補的襪子我的腳穿不進去了
Dialogue: 1,1:10:11.13,1:10:12.54,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,也有別的襪子吧
Dialogue: 1,1:10:12.65,1:10:16.53,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,兩位 這架必須得現在吵嗎
Dialogue: 1,1:10:17.87,1:10:20.48,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,又走錯路了 是這邊
Dialogue: 1,1:10:20.48,1:10:21.73,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 1,1:10:22.18,1:10:25.49,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我們家在那邊 在那座灰之峰的方向
Dialogue: 1,1:10:25.55,1:10:26.83,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,都說了我知道
Dialogue: 1,1:10:30.48,1:10:33.86,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那個冬天 雪很多
Dialogue: 1,1:10:34.65,1:10:36.36,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,真讓人期盼春天的到來
