Dialogue: 1,1:15:08.53,1:15:10.57,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,真是提不起勁
Dialogue: 1,1:15:10.76,1:15:13.28,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,畢竟那人她丈夫都已經戰死了
Dialogue: 1,1:15:13.34,1:15:16.16,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,這次連17歲的兒子也死了
Dialogue: 1,1:15:16.21,1:15:18.16,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,恭喜你了
Dialogue: 1,1:15:22.89,1:15:24.46,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,防空服裝準備好
Dialogue: 1,1:15:24.46,1:15:25.62,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,火源處理沒問題
Dialogue: 1,1:15:25.62,1:15:27.17,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,門窗和拉門拆掉
Dialogue: 1,1:15:27.33,1:15:28.40,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,防空用具
Dialogue: 1,1:15:28.41,1:15:29.09,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 1,1:15:29.56,1:15:32.11,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,真是的 太暗了都看不見了
Dialogue: 1,1:15:32.11,1:15:32.91,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 1,1:15:33.99,1:15:35.13,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 1,1:15:35.89,1:15:37.34,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,哪裡來的貓？
Dialogue: 1,1:15:43.20,1:15:45.68,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,警報已經聽膩了
Dialogue: 1,1:15:59.71,1:16:01.12,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,第一次見到
Dialogue: 1,1:16:07.54,1:16:12.88,kono-text-cn - tips,,0,0,0,,此為F-13超級堡壘拍攝到大和號出擊照片
