Dialogue: 1,1:16:19.86,1:16:24.21,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,後續目標 德島縣 東南部敵機30架
Dialogue: 1,1:16:24.25,1:16:26.37,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,逐漸前往吳市方面
Dialogue: 1,1:16:28.03,1:16:32.10,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,空襲警報解除
Dialogue: 1,1:16:32.32,1:16:33.55,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,哎
Dialogue: 1,1:16:33.56,1:16:37.63,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,5日上午 敵軍大型號125架來襲
Dialogue: 1,1:16:40.98,1:16:42.01,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 1,1:16:43.87,1:16:45.76,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,沒事吧 周作
Dialogue: 1,1:16:45.81,1:16:46.72,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,爸爸呢？
Dialogue: 1,1:16:47.78,1:16:49.40,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不 還沒
Dialogue: 1,1:16:49.58,1:16:50.47,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 1,1:16:54.36,1:16:56.74,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,鈴 冒煙了
Dialogue: 1,1:17:06.10,1:17:08.38,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,鈴真是小個
Dialogue: 1,1:17:11.70,1:17:13.51,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,站起來也很小個
Dialogue: 1,1:17:14.93,1:17:16.14,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 1,1:17:16.32,1:17:17.56,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 1,1:17:17.92,1:17:19.96,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,因為小個所以說你小個而已
Dialogue: 1,1:17:32.91,1:17:35.96,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,父親他一定沒事的
Dialogue: 1,1:17:35.96,1:17:37.04,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,軍服
Dialogue: 1,1:17:38.80,1:17:40.50,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,在包袱布裡面
Dialogue: 1,1:17:41.60,1:17:45.39,kono-text-cn - tips,,0,0,0,,註：兵曹是日本舊海軍的下級軍官
Dialogue: 1,1:17:41.60,1:17:45.39,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我在15日會升遷為法務一等兵曹
Dialogue: 1,1:17:45.79,1:17:49.30,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,因為現在是軍人了 所以會在海兵團裡接受訓練
Dialogue: 1,1:17:49.52,1:17:50.75,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,三個月內不會回來
Dialogue: 1,1:17:52.22,1:17:55.23,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那之後能回來嗎
Dialogue: 1,1:17:55.38,1:17:56.23,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,應該能
Dialogue: 1,1:17:57.44,1:17:59.72,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,沒問題吧 鈴
Dialogue: 1,1:18:00.24,1:18:02.23,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,這麼小個這麼纖細
Dialogue: 1,1:18:02.61,1:18:06.52,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,能守護住這個沒有男丁的家嗎
Dialogue: 1,1:18:07.72,1:18:08.74,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 1,1:18:09.64,1:18:10.74,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,絕對不行
Dialogue: 1,1:18:16.40,1:18:19.10,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,對不起 騙你的
Dialogue: 1,1:18:20.25,1:18:22.06,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我喜歡你
Dialogue: 1,1:18:22.92,1:18:24.99,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,但是3個月沒法見面的話
Dialogue: 1,1:18:25.00,1:18:27.16,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,可能會忘記你長什麼樣子
Dialogue: 1,1:18:27.78,1:18:28.85,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,鈴
Dialogue: 1,1:18:29.21,1:18:31.09,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,所以我會在這家裡等著
Dialogue: 1,1:18:31.55,1:18:35.87,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,因為不在這個家裡 也許我就沒法找到周作了
