Dialogue: 0,1:35:11.76,1:35:15.48,kono-zs,,0,0,0,,{\p1\c&HFFFFFF&\bord3\1a&H64&\an5\pos(548.163,760.536)}m 0 0 l 0 500 l 400 500 l 400 0\N
Dialogue: 0,1:35:11.76,1:35:15.48,kono-zs,,0,0,0,,{\p1\c&HFFFFFF&\bord3\1a&H64&\an5\pos(649.726,255.207)}m 0 0 l 0 300 l 200 300 l 200 0\N
Dialogue: 1,1:35:13.55,1:35:15.60,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,真慘啊
Dialogue: 1,1:35:26.88,1:35:30.83,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,吳市也遭受了好幾次空襲 真是可憐
Dialogue: 1,1:35:32.02,1:35:36.45,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,而且你也做不了家務了 以後會更加辛苦吧
Dialogue: 1,1:35:38.68,1:35:40.26,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我說 鈴
Dialogue: 1,1:35:41.06,1:35:43.65,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,回來廣島吧
Dialogue: 1,1:35:44.88,1:35:46.95,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,沒有嚴重的空襲
Dialogue: 1,1:35:47.13,1:35:49.08,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,鬼哥哥也已經不在了
Dialogue: 1,1:35:49.22,1:35:51.44,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,已經沒有會欺負我們的人了
Dialogue: 1,1:35:53.99,1:35:55.82,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,也不是這樣
Dialogue: 1,1:35:56.92,1:36:00.71,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我要看下你的將校先生是不是美男子再決定
Dialogue: 1,1:36:00.77,1:36:03.00,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,討厭 真是不純
Dialogue: 1,1:36:03.19,1:36:04.36,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,開玩笑開玩笑啦
Dialogue: 1,1:36:04.44,1:36:05.73,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那再見啦
Dialogue: 1,1:36:05.73,1:36:06.75,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,扭曲了
Dialogue: 1,1:36:06.88,1:36:09.36,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我倒是覺得是個不錯的想法
Dialogue: 1,1:36:09.95,1:36:12.96,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,下個月的六號是江波的祭典呢
Dialogue: 1,1:36:13.01,1:36:14.81,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,早點回來吧
Dialogue: 1,1:36:14.90,1:36:17.20,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,謝謝你 澄
Dialogue: 1,1:36:17.32,1:36:20.19,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我覺得鬼哥哥死了真是太好了
Dialogue: 1,1:36:21.14,1:36:22.83,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,扭曲了的是我
Dialogue: 1,1:36:23.60,1:36:25.82,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,就像用左手畫出來的畫一樣
Dialogue: 1,1:37:13.43,1:37:15.92,kono-text-cn-2,,0,0,0,,哎 今天也來了
Dialogue: 1,1:37:14.83,1:37:18.64,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,好像又要很久的樣子 把身邊的東西帶上吧
Dialogue: 1,1:37:18.65,1:37:18.79,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 1,1:37:18.80,1:37:19.48,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,好燙
Dialogue: 1,1:37:19.48,1:37:22.05,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,鈴 你先去吧
Dialogue: 1,1:37:29.82,1:37:31.07,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不能過來
Dialogue: 1,1:37:32.64,1:37:34.94,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,現在 不能過來這邊
Dialogue: 1,1:37:45.26,1:37:46.53,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,就是那邊
Dialogue: 1,1:37:46.60,1:37:48.30,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,往那邊一直逃
Dialogue: 1,1:37:48.75,1:37:51.45,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,越過了山 就是廣島了
Dialogue: 1,1:38:24.09,1:38:25.09,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你想死嗎
Dialogue: 1,1:38:26.38,1:38:28.52,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,對不起 鷺鷥…
Dialogue: 1,1:38:28.88,1:38:30.38,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,有隻鷺鷥飛過
Dialogue: 1,1:38:31.02,1:38:33.79,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,嗯 應該是從海邊逃過來的吧
Dialogue: 1,1:38:34.97,1:38:37.21,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,周作 我
Dialogue: 1,1:38:38.13,1:38:39.59,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,要回廣島去
Dialogue: 1,1:38:44.25,1:38:45.91,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你不想再回來了嗎
Dialogue: 1,1:38:47.40,1:38:48.95,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,是在意手的事嗎
Dialogue: 1,1:38:50.22,1:38:51.68,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,是空襲很可怕嗎
Dialogue: 1,1:38:52.05,1:38:53.61,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,還是因為晴美嗎
Dialogue: 1,1:38:53.76,1:38:56.01,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,對 對
Dialogue: 1,1:38:56.74,1:38:57.85,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,全部都對
Dialogue: 1,1:38:58.06,1:38:59.12,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我聽不到
Dialogue: 1,1:38:59.19,1:39:00.26,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不對
Dialogue: 1,1:39:01.80,1:39:03.22,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那為什麼
Dialogue: 1,1:39:04.97,1:39:08.18,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,鈴 我很幸福
Dialogue: 1,1:39:08.54,1:39:11.63,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,這一年半 能回到有你在的家
Dialogue: 1,1:39:12.27,1:39:14.15,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,無論是和你牽手散步
Dialogue: 1,1:39:14.42,1:39:15.87,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,還是和你聊天
Dialogue: 1,1:39:17.63,1:39:19.36,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,難道你就不是嗎
Dialogue: 1,1:39:19.40,1:39:21.43,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我家還是這麼陌生嗎
Dialogue: 1,1:39:24.63,1:39:25.68,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我聽不到
Dialogue: 1,1:39:26.94,1:39:28.15,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,聽不到 聽不到
Dialogue: 1,1:39:28.29,1:39:29.61,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,一句都聽不到
Dialogue: 1,1:39:29.61,1:39:31.21,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,回去 回去
Dialogue: 1,1:39:31.22,1:39:33.00,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我要回廣島去
Dialogue: 1,1:39:33.13,1:39:34.43,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,啊是嗎
Dialogue: 1,1:39:35.35,1:39:36.62,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,隨便你
Dialogue: 0,1:39:49.67,1:39:54.13,kono-hmz,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1523,1043)\frz270\pos(293.352,291.175)\c&HE7E7E6&}九天後
Dialogue: 1,1:39:49.92,1:39:52.90,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,中國軍管區內上空沒有敵機
Dialogue: 1,1:39:53.34,1:39:56.34,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,中國軍管區內上空沒有敵機
Dialogue: 1,1:39:56.74,1:40:02.02,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,廣島地區7時31分警戒警報已解除
Dialogue: 1,1:40:03.68,1:40:06.09,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,在正好的時間解除了
Dialogue: 1,1:40:06.14,1:40:07.89,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那我就先走了
Dialogue: 1,1:40:07.94,1:40:10.00,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,嗯 路上小心
Dialogue: 1,1:40:11.21,1:40:13.77,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,啊 痛痛痛…
Dialogue: 1,1:40:14.20,1:40:15.64,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,就是這裡
Dialogue: 1,1:40:16.10,1:40:19.12,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,真是的 一大早就這麼熱
Dialogue: 1,1:40:21.20,1:40:22.89,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,會很寂寞呢
Dialogue: 1,1:40:23.41,1:40:25.85,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,如果鈴不在了的話
Dialogue: 1,1:40:45.63,1:40:47.89,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,所以 是幾點
Dialogue: 1,1:40:49.26,1:40:50.22,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,醫院
Dialogue: 1,1:40:50.92,1:40:53.45,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,啊 10點左右
Dialogue: 1,1:40:57.44,1:40:58.76,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你這個打扮不行
Dialogue: 1,1:41:10.43,1:41:12.63,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不好意思 那個…
Dialogue: 1,1:41:13.90,1:41:16.51,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,啊 這個不是要洗的
Dialogue: 1,1:41:18.52,1:41:21.73,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,是今天吧 你家那邊的祭典
Dialogue: 1,1:41:22.92,1:41:23.45,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,對
Dialogue: 1,1:41:24.18,1:41:26.27,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我是打算週末回去的
Dialogue: 1,1:41:26.78,1:41:29.89,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不過醫院的預約只有今天能拿到
Dialogue: 1,1:41:33.83,1:41:35.11,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,別偷看啊
Dialogue: 1,1:41:35.12,1:41:36.12,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 1,1:41:37.64,1:41:39.61,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,反正去了也約不到
Dialogue: 1,1:41:40.25,1:41:42.18,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,醫生也是很忙的
Dialogue: 1,1:41:43.05,1:41:46.66,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,還要讓廣島的醫院寫介紹信才行
Dialogue: 1,1:41:47.72,1:41:50.27,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,再說了 汽車的車票也買不到
Dialogue: 1,1:41:53.94,1:41:57.12,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你妹妹純棉那件給你改成褲子了
Dialogue: 1,1:41:57.95,1:42:00.19,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,橡皮筋也給你縫上了 你自己穿起來吧
Dialogue: 1,1:42:00.56,1:42:02.62,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,橡皮筋是拼湊起來的抱歉了
Dialogue: 1,1:42:03.52,1:42:06.21,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,謝…謝謝
Dialogue: 1,1:42:10.28,1:42:11.36,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 1,1:42:11.90,1:42:14.57,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,把晴美的死怪在你身上
Dialogue: 1,1:42:15.90,1:42:16.63,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 1,1:42:18.87,1:42:21.42,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我喜歡的人很早就死了
Dialogue: 1,1:42:22.18,1:42:24.27,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,店也為了防火帶給拆了
Dialogue: 1,1:42:25.27,1:42:27.04,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,孩子也再也見不到了
Dialogue: 1,1:42:28.24,1:42:31.12,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不過這也是自己所選擇的道路的結果
Dialogue: 1,1:42:33.09,1:42:34.77,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,在這點上
Dialogue: 1,1:42:34.79,1:42:37.41,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你順從周圍的人嫁到了一個陌生的家裡
Dialogue: 1,1:42:37.73,1:42:39.74,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,百依百順地幹活
Dialogue: 1,1:42:41.14,1:42:43.78,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我認為那一定是很無趣的人生吧
Dialogue: 1,1:42:48.66,1:42:51.17,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,鈴的歸宿是這裡也行
Dialogue: 1,1:42:51.39,1:42:52.43,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,是哪裡都行
Dialogue: 1,1:42:53.08,1:42:55.97,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不要有太多顧慮 自己決定吧
Dialogue: 1,1:43:07.59,1:43:10.60,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,徑子 剛剛是不是哪裡發光了
Dialogue: 1,1:43:10.61,1:43:12.02,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 1,1:43:12.62,1:43:15.20,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,是打雷吧 明明天氣這麼好
Dialogue: 1,1:43:15.77,1:43:18.19,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那個 這個還是…
Dialogue: 1,1:43:18.41,1:43:20.04,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,能幫我洗嗎
Dialogue: 1,1:43:21.20,1:43:23.79,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,還有就是…
Dialogue: 1,1:43:24.39,1:43:26.74,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,能讓我待在這裡嗎
Dialogue: 1,1:43:26.80,1:43:27.49,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,啊我知道了
Dialogue: 1,1:43:27.49,1:43:30.53,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我知道了別靠過來 很熱的
Dialogue: 1,1:43:40.09,1:43:41.74,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,剛剛是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 1,1:43:44.37,1:43:47.16,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不好 JOFK什麼都聽不到
Dialogue: 1,1:43:47.17,1:43:48.35,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,情況呢
Dialogue: 1,1:43:48.62,1:43:49.54,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 1,1:43:50.81,1:43:52.25,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,來這邊看下
Dialogue: 1,1:43:56.41,1:43:59.03,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那朵雲是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 1,1:44:00.37,1:44:01.06,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,雲？
Dialogue: 1,1:44:02.28,1:44:05.79,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那朵雲很大吧 叫「砧狀積雨雲」哦
Dialogue: 1,1:44:06.40,1:44:08.22,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,這裡是岡山放送局
Dialogue: 1,1:44:08.46,1:44:11.25,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,廣島放送局？廣島放送局？
Dialogue: 1,1:44:11.78,1:44:13.38,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,這裡是岡山放送局
Dialogue: 1,1:44:13.69,1:44:18.86,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我以為掉了什麼下來 原來是廣島的傳閱板
Dialogue: 1,1:44:26.03,1:44:29.75,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,有空閒的人等下到鄰保館集合
Dialogue: 1,1:44:26.03,1:44:29.75,kono-text-cn - tips,,0,0,0,,註：鄰保館：在有貧困，教育，歧視和環境等比較惡劣的問題的區域，擁有解決這些問題的專門知識的人常駐，\n對當地人進行適當的援助的社會福利設施。
Dialogue: 1,1:44:31.47,1:44:33.93,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,知多你是護士啊
Dialogue: 1,1:44:33.94,1:44:36.97,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,是 草鞋什麼的我也沒做過
Dialogue: 1,1:44:37.44,1:44:39.55,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,這附近的人都是這樣
Dialogue: 1,1:44:39.71,1:44:41.04,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,這樣就可以了嗎
Dialogue: 1,1:44:41.04,1:44:41.57,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 1,1:44:43.41,1:44:45.78,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,單手沒法做的很好
Dialogue: 1,1:44:45.84,1:44:47.44,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你是在挖苦我嗎
Dialogue: 1,1:44:47.84,1:44:50.44,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,然後這些草鞋要做什麼的
Dialogue: 1,1:44:50.46,1:44:51.70,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,送去廣島
Dialogue: 1,1:44:51.86,1:44:54.53,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,要是和上個月的空襲一樣道路都融了的話
Dialogue: 1,1:44:54.58,1:44:56.20,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,鞋子和木屐就不能用了
Dialogue: 1,1:44:57.26,1:44:58.61,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我能跟過去嗎
Dialogue: 1,1:44:59.08,1:45:00.32,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,受傷的人不行
Dialogue: 1,1:45:00.39,1:45:03.59,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我兒子也給廣島的兵隊徵召了
Dialogue: 1,1:45:03.82,1:45:06.08,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,這樣的話要不要乘明天的卡車去
Dialogue: 1,1:45:06.38,1:45:09.42,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,吳市的空襲廣島也經常幫助我們
Dialogue: 1,1:45:09.54,1:45:11.28,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,算是報答
Dialogue: 1,1:45:14.40,1:45:15.99,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,這樣扎頭髮的時間也省下來了
Dialogue: 1,1:45:16.29,1:45:18.05,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我不會給你們添麻煩的
Dialogue: 1,1:45:18.15,1:45:18.91,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 1,1:45:19.81,1:45:20.98,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,又來 笨蛋
Dialogue: 1,1:45:20.98,1:45:23.26,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,快點回家剪整齊點
Dialogue: 1,1:45:23.62,1:45:26.34,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我家人也說近期要到廣島去
Dialogue: 1,1:45:27.69,1:45:30.31,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,好像是新型的炸彈落在了廣島
Dialogue: 1,1:45:32.21,1:45:33.78,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,鈴家裡沒事吧
Dialogue: 1,1:45:33.79,1:45:34.69,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 1,1:45:36.16,1:45:39.96,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,鎮守府也派了救援
Dialogue: 1,1:45:50.04,1:45:52.41,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你也是從廣島來的嗎
Dialogue: 1,1:46:07.69,1:46:10.38,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,就這麼坐著死去的嗎
Dialogue: 1,1:46:10.52,1:46:13.00,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,從廣島走到這邊來
Dialogue: 1,1:46:13.00,1:46:15.98,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,哎 是哪裡的誰也不知道
Dialogue: 1,1:46:16.13,1:46:18.27,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,樣子和衣服也都破破爛爛了
Dialogue: 1,1:46:18.33,1:46:20.62,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不要和北條家的妻子說起
Dialogue: 1,1:46:20.63,1:46:24.15,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那個孩子的臉都看不清了 真可憐
Dialogue: 1,1:46:27.12,1:46:29.36,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我摘了桉樹的葉子過來了
Dialogue: 1,1:46:29.73,1:46:31.47,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,請用來做蚊香
Dialogue: 1,1:46:32.65,1:46:33.96,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 1,1:46:34.58,1:46:36.13,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,要堅持下去哦
Dialogue: 1,1:46:36.38,1:46:36.87,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 1,1:46:37.19,1:46:37.80,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,然後
Dialogue: 1,1:46:38.53,1:46:41.54,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,江波的浦野十郎 喜乃 澄
Dialogue: 1,1:46:42.91,1:46:46.35,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,草津的森田絲糸 麻里奈 千鶴子
Dialogue: 1,1:46:48.35,1:46:50.14,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我也想變得堅強
Dialogue: 1,1:46:51.11,1:46:52.99,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,想要變得溫柔和頑強
Dialogue: 1,1:46:53.34,1:46:54.85,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,就像這座鎮子上的人一樣
Dialogue: 1,1:46:55.80,1:46:57.65,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,啊 好吵啊
Dialogue: 1,1:46:57.89,1:47:00.15,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我是不會屈服於這樣的暴力的
Dialogue: 1,1:47:00.89,1:47:03.39,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fn@方正中等线_GBK\b1\c&H393535&\bord0\fs40\frz270\pos(1863.369,777.612)}告日本國民書 請立即離開城市
Dialogue: 1,1:47:00.89,1:47:03.39,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fn@方正中等线_GBK\c&H393535&\bord0\fs40\frz270\pos(1578.788,803.766)}這張傳單上寫的事情十分重要\h\h\n請務必認真閱讀。\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\n各位日本國民現在面臨著一個\h\h\n十分嚴峻的秋天。軍部高層的\h\h\n傢伙已經無視了「十三條之寬\h\h\n大條款」給予日本停止無謂的\h\h\n戰爭的機會。\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h
Dialogue: 1,1:47:00.89,1:47:03.39,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fn@方正中等线_GBK\c&H393535&\bord0\fs40\frz270\pos(1540.259,746.674)}為此蘇聯已經對日本宣戰。
Dialogue: 1,1:47:00.89,1:47:03.39,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fn@方正中等线_GBK\c&H393535&\bord0\fs40\frz270\pos(1337.198,818.887)}並且美國已經發明並使用了無論\h\h\n多少人都無法匹敵的原子彈。\h\h\h\n這種原子彈僅一個就能與兩千架\h\h\n巨大的B-29轟炸機投下的炸彈\h\h\h\n匹敵\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h
Dialogue: 0,1:47:00.89,1:47:03.39,kono-text-cn - tips,,0,0,0,,註：十三條之寬大條款指的是「波茨坦公告」
Dialogue: 0,1:47:00.89,1:47:03.39,kono-zs,,0,0,0,,{\p1\c&HFFFFFF&\bord3\1a&H64&\an5\pos(1641.777,784.568)}m 0 0 l 0 500 l 650 500 l 650 0\N
Dialogue: 1,1:47:01.76,1:47:04.83,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,請讓我一直待在這裡
Dialogue: 1,1:47:06.54,1:47:08.09,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,老是讓人擔心
Dialogue: 1,1:47:08.38,1:47:09.66,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你這個笨蛋
Dialogue: 1,1:47:09.99,1:47:12.39,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,笨蛋 笨蛋 笨蛋 笨…
Dialogue: 1,1:47:13.00,1:47:14.58,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 1,1:47:15.89,1:47:16.68,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 1,1:47:17.50,1:47:18.97,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,非常對不起
Dialogue: 1,1:47:20.18,1:47:21.35,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 1,1:47:21.59,1:47:23.42,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,一個都打不中
Dialogue: 1,1:47:23.69,1:47:26.04,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,這樣又要給海兵團的人欺負了
Dialogue: 1,1:47:27.32,1:47:28.46,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,鈴
Dialogue: 1,1:47:28.68,1:47:31.20,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,撿到美軍的傳單不交上去的話
Dialogue: 1,1:47:31.29,1:47:33.37,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,又會被憲兵們斥責的
Dialogue: 1,1:47:34.21,1:47:36.57,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,就算交上去也只是被燒了而已
Dialogue: 1,1:47:36.88,1:47:40.71,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,像這樣做成廁紙還更加有用
Dialogue: 1,1:47:40.99,1:47:42.02,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,說的也是
Dialogue: 1,1:47:42.75,1:47:45.23,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不過暫時廁所就不能借給外人就是了
Dialogue: 1,1:47:45.63,1:47:49.72,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,用盡所有方法生存下去就是我的戰鬥了
Dialogue: 1,1:47:52.20,1:47:53.38,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,請進
Dialogue: 1,1:47:53.38,1:47:54.42,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,打擾了
Dialogue: 1,1:47:54.83,1:47:58.35,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,死於戰陣 殉於職守
Dialogue: 1,1:47:58.37,1:48:04.06,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,斃於非命者及其遺屬
Dialogue: 1,1:48:04.24,1:48:06.00,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,則五臟為之俱裂
Dialogue: 1,1:48:06.01,1:48:10.41,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,至於負戰傷 蒙戰禍
Dialogue: 1,1:48:10.43,1:48:13.70,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,失家業者之生計
Dialogue: 1,1:48:13.78,1:48:17.97,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,忍所難忍 耐所難耐
Dialogue: 1,1:48:17.99,1:48:20.44,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,以為萬世之太平
Dialogue: 1,1:48:20.26,1:48:25.53,kono-text-cn-2,,0,0,0,,天皇陛下的玉音已恭敬地播送完畢
Dialogue: 1,1:48:23.38,1:48:25.75,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,結束了結束了
Dialogue: 1,1:48:25.85,1:48:26.98,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,這個是
Dialogue: 1,1:48:27.15,1:48:29.31,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,就是輸了的意思嗎
Dialogue: 1,1:48:30.18,1:48:31.16,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 1,1:48:31.16,1:48:34.40,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,廣島和長崎都給投放了新型的炸彈
Dialogue: 1,1:48:34.41,1:48:38.15,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,蘇聯也參戰了 打不過的
Dialogue: 1,1:48:39.21,1:48:41.70,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,這不是都已經做好覺悟了嗎
Dialogue: 1,1:48:42.15,1:48:45.02,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不是說要戰鬥到最後一個人嗎
Dialogue: 1,1:48:45.47,1:48:47.69,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,現在這裡就還有五個人
Dialogue: 1,1:48:47.98,1:48:51.26,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我還有左手 雙腳還留著
Dialogue: 1,1:48:59.27,1:49:00.52,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,晴美
Dialogue: 1,1:49:01.46,1:49:03.25,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,晴美
Dialogue: 1,1:49:10.70,1:49:12.22,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,都飛走了
Dialogue: 1,1:49:12.47,1:49:13.98,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我至今為止的一切
Dialogue: 1,1:49:14.89,1:49:17.15,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我認為很好的東西
Dialogue: 1,1:49:17.85,1:49:20.86,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,所以一直忍耐著的理由
Dialogue: 1,1:49:23.33,1:49:27.00,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,從海的對面過來的大米 大豆
Dialogue: 1,1:49:27.01,1:49:30.18,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我們是用這些東西做成的嗎
Dialogue: 1,1:49:31.52,1:49:34.62,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,所以我們就得屈服於暴力嗎
Dialogue: 1,1:49:37.69,1:49:42.36,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,真想什麼都不去考慮 就在迷糊中死去
Dialogue: 1,1:49:55.32,1:50:00.08,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,這是萬一到了最後的時候 給大家存著的
Dialogue: 1,1:50:01.53,1:50:04.14,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,今天就什麼都不加地煮吧
Dialogue: 1,1:50:04.60,1:50:06.26,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不能全部煮掉就是了
Dialogue: 1,1:50:06.38,1:50:10.07,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,還有明天和後天呢
Dialogue: 1,1:50:15.87,1:50:22.66,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,8月15日 16日 17日
Dialogue: 1,1:50:24.43,1:50:27.85,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,9月 10月
Dialogue: 1,1:50:28.43,1:50:30.39,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,11月和下一年
Dialogue: 1,1:50:31.63,1:50:34.48,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,再下一年 10年後也
Dialogue: 1,1:50:35.61,1:50:37.72,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,一直 一直
Dialogue: 1,1:50:49.16,1:50:51.42,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,白得閃閃發亮呢
Dialogue: 1,1:50:51.75,1:50:53.70,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不過沒有什麼配菜
Dialogue: 1,1:50:53.85,1:50:54.87,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 1,1:50:55.33,1:50:56.44,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,周作呢
Dialogue: 1,1:50:56.61,1:50:57.44,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,還沒回來
Dialogue: 1,1:50:57.89,1:51:02.17,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,事已至此 作為法務部的工作就更應該守護好秩序嗎
Dialogue: 1,1:51:02.98,1:51:04.39,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我們先開動吧
Dialogue: 1,1:51:06.89,1:51:09.78,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,再也沒炸彈落下 所以也沒有浮上來的魚了
Dialogue: 1,1:51:10.07,1:51:11.80,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那個時候
Dialogue: 1,1:51:23.49,1:51:25.26,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你在做什麼呢
Dialogue: 1,1:51:25.29,1:51:27.56,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,難得的白米飯都看不見了
Dialogue: 1,1:51:40.40,1:51:42.14,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,終於上陸了
Dialogue: 1,1:51:42.79,1:51:44.46,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我要調動到大竹去
Dialogue: 1,1:51:45.32,1:51:47.46,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,到海軍解體為止
Dialogue: 1,1:51:47.52,1:51:51.68,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,無論發生什麼 都要守護好秩序就是法務部的工作
Dialogue: 1,1:51:53.74,1:51:56.47,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,這種時候 要是有雙手的話
Dialogue: 1,1:51:56.56,1:52:01.06,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,就能輕輕地握住他不安的手了
Dialogue: 1,1:52:02.82,1:52:04.04,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,真是安靜呢
Dialogue: 1,1:52:04.04,1:52:05.61,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,大家都準備好了
Dialogue: 1,1:52:06.29,1:52:08.77,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不好意思了 到這裡就行了
Dialogue: 1,1:52:10.35,1:52:12.19,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,早點回家去吧
Dialogue: 1,1:52:13.19,1:52:14.08,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,再見了
Dialogue: 1,1:52:17.22,1:52:19.27,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我絕對會回來的
Dialogue: 1,1:52:19.56,1:52:20.88,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,回到鈴的身邊
Dialogue: 1,1:52:22.20,1:52:22.81,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,1:52:24.05,1:52:27.51,kono-hmz,,0,0,0,,{\fn@方正粗圆_gbk\frz291.8\pos(1324,404)\c&H9A9FA4&\fad(1022,0)}明天的米飯配給延期了
Dialogue: 1,1:52:25.36,1:52:28.65,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,鹽和醬油一直都沒有
Dialogue: 0,1:52:28.05,1:52:33.01,kono-hmz,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1523,681)\fs50\fn方正粗雅宋_GBK\c&HE7E5E5&\pos(347.022,221.155)}1945
Dialogue: 0,1:52:28.05,1:52:33.01,kono-hmz,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1523,681)\fs70\fn@方正粗雅宋_GBK\frz270.8\c&HE7E5E5&\pos(349.466,290.91)}年
Dialogue: 0,1:52:28.05,1:52:33.01,kono-hmz,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1523,681)\fs60\fn@方正粗雅宋_GBK\c&HE7E5E5&\pos(343.693,363.289)}11
Dialogue: 0,1:52:28.05,1:52:33.01,kono-hmz,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1523,681)\fs70\fn@方正粗雅宋_GBK\frz270.8\c&HE7E5E5&\pos(348.396,431.739)}月
Dialogue: 1,1:52:34.08,1:52:35.39,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,啊 姐姐
Dialogue: 1,1:52:35.39,1:52:36.49,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,啊 鈴
Dialogue: 1,1:52:36.65,1:52:38.53,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,這是什麼的隊伍
Dialogue: 1,1:52:38.64,1:52:40.99,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不知道 什麼都行
Dialogue: 1,1:52:40.99,1:52:43.03,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,反正什麼都缺
Dialogue: 1,1:52:43.67,1:52:44.88,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,嘛 說的也是
Dialogue: 1,1:52:46.23,1:52:49.15,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不過這座鎮子也變了呢
Dialogue: 1,1:52:49.77,1:52:51.02,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,give me
Dialogue: 1,1:52:51.16,1:52:53.81,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,久夫現在也在模仿著那種事嗎
Dialogue: 1,1:52:54.87,1:52:56.25,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,晴美也會做嗎
Dialogue: 1,1:52:56.26,1:53:00.07,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,是占領軍的剩菜雜煮
Dialogue: 1,1:53:02.52,1:53:03.84,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,還有紙屑
Dialogue: 1,1:53:15.01,1:53:17.11,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 1,1:53:19.74,1:53:22.08,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,這邊就完全沒有味道
Dialogue: 1,1:53:23.59,1:53:26.63,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,然後我跟美國人指路後
Dialogue: 1,1:53:26.90,1:53:28.46,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,就給了我巧克力
Dialogue: 1,1:53:28.69,1:53:32.35,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你也剪著這個髮型 應該是把你當小孩子了吧
Dialogue: 1,1:53:38.16,1:53:39.59,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,可以嗎
Dialogue: 1,1:53:39.71,1:53:41.99,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,拿那麼多洋服去換
Dialogue: 1,1:53:42.46,1:53:43.72,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,沒事哦
Dialogue: 1,1:53:44.51,1:53:45.75,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你不知道吧
Dialogue: 1,1:53:46.42,1:53:49.03,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,死在鄰保館旁的士兵
Dialogue: 1,1:53:49.13,1:53:51.12,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,好像是我的孩子
Dialogue: 1,1:53:52.23,1:53:54.69,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,自己的孩子我都沒能認出來
Dialogue: 1,1:53:56.80,1:53:59.22,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,在你面前晴美也
Dialogue: 1,1:54:00.57,1:54:01.26,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 1,1:54:02.10,1:54:03.16,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,很遺憾
Dialogue: 1,1:54:07.10,1:54:07.83,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,鈴
Dialogue: 1,1:54:10.14,1:54:10.91,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,鈴
Dialogue: 1,1:54:12.10,1:54:13.90,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,想念我的話
Dialogue: 1,1:54:14.58,1:54:16.03,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,就笑吧
Dialogue: 1,1:54:18.59,1:54:22.76,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,在這個世界普通地 認真地居住下去吧
Dialogue: 1,1:54:24.02,1:54:24.76,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,鈴
Dialogue: 1,1:54:25.35,1:54:26.44,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,晴美
Dialogue: 1,1:54:26.91,1:54:29.70,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我看見那裡有什麼船了 晴美
Dialogue: 1,1:54:31.03,1:54:33.64,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,在那裡的是 青葉
Dialogue: 1,1:54:35.95,1:54:36.77,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,哲
Dialogue: 1,1:54:37.71,1:54:40.14,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,現在在你笑容的盡頭
Dialogue: 1,1:54:40.71,1:54:46.56,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,寄宿著跳動著兔子的大海 飛翔著鷺鷥的天空
Dialogue: 1,1:54:51.10,1:54:53.14,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,晴美笑的很開心
Dialogue: 1,1:54:53.28,1:54:56.90,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我也要笑著想起晴美的事
Dialogue: 1,1:54:57.17,1:55:01.10,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,這之後 我要一直當笑容的化身
Dialogue: 1,1:55:01.59,1:55:05.17,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,是呀 一直哭就太浪費了
Dialogue: 1,1:55:05.86,1:55:07.75,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,浪費鹽分
Dialogue: 1,1:55:09.14,1:55:12.18,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,真是多虧了海裡的鹽分呢
Dialogue: 1,1:55:12.58,1:55:15.88,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,婆婆 婆婆 千鶴子
Dialogue: 0,1:55:12.88,1:55:17.89,kono-text-year,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1523,681)\fs50\fn方正粗雅宋_GBK\c&HE7E5E5&\bord0.1\blur5\pos(1570.442,184.327)}1946
Dialogue: 0,1:55:12.88,1:55:17.89,kono-text-year,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1523,681)\fs70\fn@方正粗雅宋_GBK\frz270.8\c&HE7E5E5&\bord0.1\blur5\pos(1544.062,222.057)}年
Dialogue: 0,1:55:12.88,1:55:17.89,kono-text-year,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1523,681)\fs60\fn@方正粗雅宋_GBK\c&HE7E5E5&\bord0.1\blur5\pos(1574.112,323.45)}1
Dialogue: 0,1:55:12.88,1:55:17.89,kono-text-year,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1523,681)\fs70\fn@方正粗雅宋_GBK\frz270.8\c&HE7E5E5&\bord0.1\blur5\pos(1543.686,365.083)}月
Dialogue: 1,1:55:17.36,1:55:18.43,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,鈴
Dialogue: 1,1:55:20.84,1:55:21.84,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,澄
Dialogue: 1,1:55:23.08,1:55:24.27,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,鈴
Dialogue: 1,1:55:24.49,1:55:26.23,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你剪頭髮了呢
Dialogue: 1,1:55:26.46,1:55:28.20,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,沒事沒事 不用起來
Dialogue: 1,1:55:28.44,1:55:29.70,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,身體不舒服嗎
Dialogue: 1,1:55:30.18,1:55:32.20,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,稍微有點頭暈而已
Dialogue: 1,1:55:33.19,1:55:35.69,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,哎 真是懊悔啊姐姐
Dialogue: 1,1:55:35.90,1:55:39.98,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,在這寒冷的天空沒法幫忙海苔的工作
Dialogue: 1,1:55:42.25,1:55:45.22,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你不好好睡也不行
Dialogue: 1,1:55:49.60,1:55:55.51,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,要是手還在就能畫鬼哥哥的南洋冒險記了
Dialogue: 1,1:55:55.84,1:55:57.04,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那是怎樣的
Dialogue: 1,1:55:57.22,1:55:58.75,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,什麼樣的故事
Dialogue: 1,1:55:59.05,1:56:02.54,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,鬼哥哥的運輸船遇難
Dialogue: 1,1:56:03.51,1:56:07.25,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,在南邊的島上用椰子葉做了個家
Dialogue: 1,1:56:07.93,1:56:09.66,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,滿臉鬍鬚
Dialogue: 1,1:56:10.17,1:56:12.02,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,娶了鱷魚做老婆
Dialogue: 1,1:56:12.19,1:56:14.37,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,鱷魚是老婆嗎
Dialogue: 1,1:56:15.92,1:56:18.67,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,會不會回來江波呢 鬼哥哥
Dialogue: 1,1:56:19.22,1:56:20.25,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,媽媽也…
Dialogue: 1,1:56:22.14,1:56:27.15,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那個早上 媽媽要做祭典的準備就去了趟鎮子
Dialogue: 1,1:56:28.61,1:56:31.24,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,雖然爸爸和我到處找過了
Dialogue: 1,1:56:31.48,1:56:33.19,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,也沒能找到
Dialogue: 1,1:56:33.86,1:56:37.63,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,爸爸十月就倒下了 馬上就死去了
Dialogue: 1,1:56:38.15,1:56:40.48,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,連同學校一起火化了
Dialogue: 1,1:56:41.20,1:56:43.96,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,沒時間通知你真是抱歉
Dialogue: 1,1:56:45.75,1:56:48.34,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,沒能早點回來對不起
Dialogue: 1,1:56:48.95,1:56:50.92,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你沒早點回來太好了
Dialogue: 1,1:56:51.82,1:56:54.80,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,鈴 我變成這樣了
Dialogue: 1,1:56:55.52,1:56:57.78,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我 能治好嗎
Dialogue: 1,1:56:57.87,1:56:58.83,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,能治好的
Dialogue: 1,1:56:59.03,1:57:00.63,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,治不好就太奇怪了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,----插曲----
Dialogue: 1,1:57:03.52,1:57:09.13,kono-chaqu-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\blur5}明明叫做冬天
Dialogue: 1,1:57:09.50,1:57:18.76,kono-chaqu-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\blur5}卻吹起了溫暖的風
Dialogue: 1,1:57:21.38,1:57:33.65,kono-chaqu-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\blur5}時而帶來大海的味道
Dialogue: 1,1:57:42.10,1:57:48.26,kono-chaqu-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\blur5}路上的碎片
Dialogue: 1,1:57:48.26,1:57:52.46,kono-chaqu-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\blur5}在一閃一閃地笑著
Dialogue: 1,1:57:53.42,1:58:03.30,kono-chaqu-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\blur5}太陽的手掌輕撫著你的後背
Dialogue: 1,1:58:16.73,1:58:22.61,kono-chaqu-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\blur5}海苔的幽暗將你懷抱
Dialogue: 1,1:58:39.40,1:58:45.34,kono-chaqu-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\blur5}再也聽不到麻雀間的談話
Dialogue: 1,1:58:49.67,1:58:55.52,kono-chaqu-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\blur5}也無法沐浴蒲公英的絨毛
Dialogue: 1,1:58:55.95,1:59:02.69,kono-chaqu-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\blur5}到達不了雲縫形成的向陽處
Dialogue: 1,1:59:02.69,1:59:12.87,kono-chaqu-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\blur5}無法知曉身旁入夢人的夢境
Dialogue: 1,1:59:14.91,1:59:23.92,kono-chaqu-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\blur5}也無法踏入每天走過的道路
Dialogue: 1,1:59:27.87,1:59:30.93,kono-chaqu-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\blur5}以越來越快的速度
Dialogue: 1,1:59:30.93,1:59:34.06,kono-chaqu-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\blur5}變成了記憶
Dialogue: 1,1:59:34.22,1:59:40.90,kono-chaqu-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\blur5}那些閃閃發亮的日子
Dialogue: 1,1:59:43.27,1:59:45.40,kono-chaqu-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\blur5}而你
Dialogue: 1,1:59:45.87,1:59:53.49,kono-chaqu-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\blur5}卻無能為力
Dialogue: 1,1:59:54.96,2:00:00.54,kono-chaqu-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\blur5}你不過是這個世界的
Dialogue: 1,2:00:00.54,2:00:05.03,kono-chaqu-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\blur5}一小部分而已
Dialogue: 1,2:00:05.93,2:00:10.92,kono-chaqu-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\blur5}是懷念你的
Dialogue: 1,2:00:10.92,2:00:18.00,kono-chaqu-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\blur5}零零碎碎的人和物
Dialogue: 1,2:00:23.78,2:00:29.80,kono-chaqu-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\blur5}拼湊集結起來的而已
Dialogue: 1,2:00:32.22,2:00:33.33,kono-chaqu-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\blur5}所以
Dialogue: 1,2:00:33.33,2:00:34.74,kono-chaqu-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\blur5}無論何時
Dialogue: 1,2:00:34.99,2:00:37.81,kono-chaqu-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\blur5}都準備著
Dialogue: 1,2:00:37.88,2:00:42.42,kono-chaqu-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\blur5}你的容身之所
Dialogue: 1,2:00:49.08,2:00:54.30,kono-chaqu-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\blur5}無論何處都寄宿著愛
Dialogue: 1,2:00:54.30,2:00:59.81,kono-chaqu-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\blur5}無論何處都寄宿著愛
Dialogue: 1,2:01:00.29,2:01:05.48,kono-chaqu-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\blur5}在不斷變換著的這個世界
Dialogue: 1,2:01:05.86,2:01:11.57,kono-chaqu-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\blur5}到處寄宿著
Dialogue: 1,2:01:14.67,2:01:20.09,kono-chaqu-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\blur5}零零散散的愛
Dialogue: 1,2:01:24.92,2:01:27.57,kono-chaqu-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\blur5}你看
Dialogue: 1,2:01:27.62,2:01:30.77,kono-chaqu-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\blur5}現在那裡也
Dialogue: 1,2:01:31.08,2:01:33.35,kono-chaqu-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\blur5}變成了你的
Dialogue: 1,2:01:33.35,2:01:38.22,kono-chaqu-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\blur5}一部分
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,----插曲----
Dialogue: 1,1:57:08.38,1:57:09.49,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,幸子
Dialogue: 1,1:57:10.60,1:57:11.33,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 1,1:57:14.76,1:57:17.52,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,清子 你是清子對吧
Dialogue: 1,1:57:19.46,1:57:23.40,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,這個鎮子大家都在找尋著不見了的某人
Dialogue: 1,1:57:23.99,1:57:28.21,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我也有兩三次找到了玲的錯覺
Dialogue: 1,1:57:29.91,1:57:30.87,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,鈴
Dialogue: 1,1:57:34.17,1:57:35.66,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你平安回來了
Dialogue: 1,1:57:36.44,1:57:39.04,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,海軍十一月也大部分解散了
Dialogue: 1,1:57:39.13,1:57:40.16,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不用工作了
Dialogue: 1,1:57:41.72,1:57:42.68,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,鈴
Dialogue: 1,1:57:43.70,1:57:47.93,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我第一次遇見鈴 就是在這橋上
Dialogue: 1,1:57:49.16,1:57:51.24,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不過已經回不到那個時候了
Dialogue: 1,1:57:51.91,1:57:55.45,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,這座城鎮和我們也會一直改變著吧
Dialogue: 1,1:57:55.67,1:57:57.95,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我無論何時都能認出鈴
Dialogue: 1,1:57:58.44,1:58:01.15,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你這裡有顆痣 馬上就能認出來
Dialogue: 1,1:58:02.40,1:58:04.41,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,周作 謝謝你
Dialogue: 1,1:58:04.87,1:58:08.34,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,在這世界的一隅找到我
Dialogue: 1,1:58:08.85,1:58:10.90,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,請不要離開我
Dialogue: 1,1:58:11.24,1:58:13.40,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,請一直陪在我身邊
Dialogue: 1,1:59:25.67,1:59:27.04,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,沒事沒事沒事
Dialogue: 1,1:59:27.28,1:59:30.94,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,總而言之 在廣島找到工作太好了
Dialogue: 1,1:59:30.94,1:59:31.49,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 1,1:59:35.03,1:59:38.30,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不過很遠很麻煩呢
Dialogue: 1,1:59:38.30,1:59:39.37,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 1,1:59:43.89,1:59:47.58,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,謝謝你 沒事哦 你吃吧
Dialogue: 1,1:59:47.83,1:59:51.32,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,要不離開這邊的家去那邊生活吧
Dialogue: 1,1:59:51.86,1:59:54.38,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你還有媽媽和澄
Dialogue: 1,1:59:54.74,1:59:58.78,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不不 我從這邊過去就好
Dialogue: 1,1:59:58.99,2:00:01.32,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,雖然也很擔心廣島的事
Dialogue: 1,2:00:01.60,2:00:04.89,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不過吳是我選擇的地方
Dialogue: 1,2:00:24.77,2:00:28.38,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,吳市 吳市
Dialogue: 1,2:00:28.38,2:00:29.15,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,吳市？
Dialogue: 1,2:00:29.87,2:00:32.17,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,對哦 這裡是吳市
Dialogue: 1,2:00:32.64,2:00:35.02,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,被九座山峰守護著
Dialogue: 1,2:00:35.39,2:00:37.39,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,所以叫做「九嶺」
Dialogue: 1,2:00:35.39,2:00:37.39,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(1058.488,917.514)}吳市
Dialogue: 1,2:00:37.90,2:00:40.61,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,右邊的是休山
Dialogue: 1,2:00:40.78,2:00:42.75,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,左邊的是缽卷山
Dialogue: 1,2:00:44.15,2:00:47.83,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,然後 正中間的是灰之峰
Dialogue: 1,2:00:50.91,2:00:53.95,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那個山麓 就是我們的家了
Dialogue: 1,2:01:03.00,2:01:04.63,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,這個孩子
Dialogue: 1,2:01:06.27,2:01:08.53,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,好多蝨子啊
Dialogue: 1,2:01:09.17,2:01:13.04,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,燒鍋開水 穿的東西也全都燙一遍
Dialogue: 1,2:01:13.41,2:01:15.47,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,總而言之先洗個澡吧
Dialogue: 1,2:01:15.47,2:01:18.16,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,這個孩子最後洗好點吧
Dialogue: 1,2:01:18.24,2:01:19.62,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,總而言之先去浴室點火
Dialogue: 1,2:01:19.63,2:01:20.32,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 1,2:01:21.41,2:01:25.05,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,去年晴美的衣服 會不會有點小
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,----ed----
Dialogue: 1,2:01:59.41,2:02:04.12,kono-ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}鳥兒運來的種子
Dialogue: 1,2:02:04.23,2:02:08.59,kono-ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}在靜悄悄地呼吸著
Dialogue: 1,2:02:09.23,2:02:13.51,kono-ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}它會帶來什麼樣的景色呢
Dialogue: 1,2:02:13.51,2:02:19.72,kono-ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}在這土地中想像下吧
Dialogue: 1,2:02:27.51,2:02:31.79,kono-ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}悄悄地偷看下吧
Dialogue: 1,2:02:32.44,2:02:36.82,kono-ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}雖然有點可怕
Dialogue: 1,2:02:37.20,2:02:41.54,kono-ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}不過我想看到充滿陽光的世界
Dialogue: 1,2:02:41.62,2:02:47.88,kono-ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}這份心情是不會動搖的
Dialogue: 1,2:02:51.38,2:02:59.93,kono-ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}風的音色改變了的話
Dialogue: 1,2:03:01.28,2:03:11.73,kono-ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}雨的荊棘不見了的話
Dialogue: 1,2:03:30.03,2:03:34.38,kono-ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}這個世界在你的眼裡
Dialogue: 1,2:03:34.59,2:03:39.26,kono-ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}看起來是什麼樣的呢
Dialogue: 1,2:03:39.45,2:03:44.06,kono-ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我在這裡生根發芽
Dialogue: 1,2:03:44.23,2:03:49.01,kono-ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}在夢中的嘆息
Dialogue: 1,2:03:49.02,2:04:05.04,kono-ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}將我的絨毛
Dialogue: 1,2:04:05.16,2:04:09.92,kono-ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}吹向遠方
Dialogue: 1,2:04:31.26,2:04:35.03,kono-ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}無法實現的願望
Dialogue: 1,2:04:36.19,2:04:39.86,kono-ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}傳達不到的思念
Dialogue: 1,2:04:40.68,2:04:45.29,kono-ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}變成深深的顏色
Dialogue: 1,2:04:45.33,2:04:52.25,kono-ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}悄悄地將我浸染
Dialogue: 1,2:04:54.23,2:04:58.01,kono-ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}越過那個屋頂
Dialogue: 1,2:04:59.06,2:05:02.55,kono-ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}到旁邊的城鎮
Dialogue: 1,2:05:03.93,2:05:12.81,kono-ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}在不知何人的院子裡
Dialogue: 1,2:05:13.81,2:05:17.19,kono-ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}不知多少在地上
Dialogue: 1,2:05:18.65,2:05:22.28,kono-ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}不知多少在船上
Dialogue: 1,2:05:23.51,2:05:33.71,kono-ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}只要到達了你的肩膀
Dialogue: 1,2:05:50.72,2:05:55.08,kono-ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}小小的火苗就會燃燒
Dialogue: 1,2:05:55.64,2:06:00.07,kono-ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}在土地上沒有一絲聲響
Dialogue: 1,2:06:00.57,2:06:04.87,kono-ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}明天自由之時到來的話
Dialogue: 1,2:06:04.90,2:06:12.46,kono-ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}便定能與你相見
